snippet.textDisplay:
Earlier,  'We are the World' brought countries together... Now, its 'Pasoori'. 
Also, I've seen / heard most of the covers done in this compilation, and each of them has put tremendous emotion into their respective versions. That's the beauty of Pasoori - you cannot, cannot, sing it without the emotions it brings out. 
Endless applause for Ali, Shea, Xulfi...the entire bts gang - I still feel they don't realise the cult they've created in the process of making it. This is surely beyond boundaries and  binaries!
